            <label><input type="radio" name="soup" value="no"> 不要湯，乾的就好</label>
        </div>

        <div class="question-group">
            <div class="question-title">Q2: 主食想要吃飯，還是麵食/其他？</div>
            <label><input type="radio" name="rice" value="yes" checked> 要吃飯（便當、丼飯）</label>
            <label><input type="radio" name="rice" value="no"> 吃麵或其它澱粉（拉麵、披薩）</label>
        </div>

        <div class="question-group">
            <div class="question-title">Q3: 想吃邪惡重口味，還是清淡點？</div>
            <label><input type="radio" name="heavy" value="yes" checked> 越邪惡、越滿足越好！</label>
            <label><input type="radio" name="heavy" value="no"> 偏向清淡健康</label>
        </div>

        <button type="button" onclick="drawLunch()">啟動命運之輪 🎲</button>
    </form>

    <div id="result-box">
